{"tid":1238543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英: 修訂《逃犯條例》重創香港在國外的聲譽","createTime":"2019-06-18T00:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:44:12.000Z","uid":241594,"like":34,"dislike":1206,"uniUserReply":156,"replies":[{"pid":"9234be848ca268c2cbfeea433ee5d732f7cfa314","tid":1238543,"uid":241594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》引起的風波，重創香港在國外的聲譽。<br />\n對外的解釋說明工作，我們不能僅靠中國駐外的使領館，不能僅靠力量單薄的香港特區經貿辦事處，更不能靠外國傳媒，我建議香港各大商會馬上組團連續出訪。各商會在特區政府作出讓步後接受修改方案，對整件事的來龍去脈最為清楚，因此最有發言權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPftjRn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPftjRn.png&h=624c2cdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7c52bc147be930898a7de01fce37c56d00378ee","tid":1238543,"uid":103481,"like":507,"dislike":2,"score":505,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:47:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦狼狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddac1a6445a768df4f0365cdcfd3167c8ee60b46","tid":1238543,"uid":392,"like":319,"dislike":1,"score":318,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:48:18.000Z","msg":"終於出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdad0b2385034d71c2ace595cdf92e616ce7ebb","tid":1238543,"uid":3457,"like":366,"dislike":3,"score":363,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:48:53.000Z","msg":"重創支那在外聲譽 唔係在港"},{"pid":"cd4333b96c29d25502be15ee95dea9d462e9bb88","tid":1238543,"uid":157735,"like":685,"dislike":2,"score":683,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:49:07.000Z","msg":"梁振英同林鄭只係地獄唔同層嘅鄰友"},{"pid":"456ffb0a6912af5d0f136f536b67d45d4f3d894f","tid":1238543,"uid":26050,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"打落水狗咁話喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e717030f67477c7d4361ba7a8a817657f0f3ec91","tid":1238543,"uid":82640,"like":176,"dislike":1,"score":175,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:4